        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/4/7/2",
        "text": [
          " في هذه الآية: يَمْحُوا اللَّهُ مَا يَشَاءُ وَيُثْبِتُ قال: فقال: وهل يمحى إلا ما كان ثابتا؟ وهل يثبت إلا ما لم يكن؟"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.ammaar-muslim": [
            "2. [2/360] al-Kafi: Ali b. Ibrahim from his father from Ibn Abi Umayr from Hisham b. Salim and Hafs b. al-Bakhtari and others apart from them both from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام that he (the Imam) said concerning the verse: “Allah erases what He wills and establishes” <a href=\"/books/quran:13#h39\">[13:39]</a> - Does He erase other than that which was established (before)? And does He establish other than that which was not there (at all)?"
          ]
        }
      },
